  geom_histogram(aes(y=..density..), bins = 30, col="black", alpha=0.3, fill="grey")+
  geom_density(lwd=1)+
  xlab("Fish Length (cm)")

#by period
ggplot(scre[!is.na(scre$FishLength),], aes(x=FishLength, group=SurveyPeriod)) + 
  geom_histogram(aes(y=..density..), bins = 30, col="black", alpha=0.3, fill="grey")+
  geom_density(lwd=1)+
  facet_wrap(~SurveyPeriod)+

  geom_density(lwd=1)+

  scale_y_continuous(limits=c(0,0.006))

    3.4 Realised fecundity

    # formula:: RF == relative fecundity - mean atretic loss

RF = round(Rel_fec - MAL, digits = 2)

RF
    ## [1] 1267.98

    3.4.1 Potential fecundity lost (n/g)

    # formula:: PFL == relative fecundity(median) - realised fecundity

PFL = Rel_fec - RF

PFL
    ## [1] 45.02

    3.4.2 Potential fecundity lost per day (n/g)
